metric: data points over time range | compare data-points over time

Aws-CloudWatch: visualisation/monitoring tool associated with diff aws services.
	- collect data(log/stat) -> display in-build metrics, stats data -> monitor -> act
Dashboard:
	- create dashboard for insight of your applications.
Alarm:
	lets say EC2 instance can be upto 75% and an Alarm should be evoked once it crosses the range.
	There are 3 alarm states:
    OK – Within Threshold.
    ALARM – Crossed Threshold.
    INSUFFICIENT_DATA – Metric not available/ Missing data (Good, Bad, Ignore, Missing).
